    <title ixia_locid="1">Performing a System Restore</title>
    <shortdesc ixia_locid="2">You can restore a HP Helion OpenStack Carrier Grade cluster from available system data
        and Cinder volume backup files to bring it back to the operational state it was when the
        backup procedure took place.</shortdesc>
    <prolog>
        <author ixia_locid="278">Jim Owens</author>
        <author></author>
    </prolog>
    <taskbody>
